# Hermes Command Center — Webhook Configuration
# Add your Discord webhook URLs here (one per line)
# Format: CHANNEL_NAME_WEBHOOK=https://discord.com/api/webhooks/...
#
# To create a webhook:
#   1. Go to the Discord channel
#   2. Edit Channel -> Integrations -> Webhooks -> New Webhook
#   3. Copy the webhook URL
#   4. Paste it below

